name: An Insane Skate Dog - A True Skater Adventure
name_original: An Insane Skate Dog - A True Skater Adventure
description:
Join the fun and adventure as Insane Skate Dog travels for fun! Enjoy the trip and skate away!

Skate away and travel those brick roads while collecting those coins along the way. You can also do some moves as you skate and jump from time to time. Do some exhibitions and have fun!

This is a fun and simple game that you will definitely enjoy!

Game Features:
> Simple game for all
> Easy control
> Fun and exciting game
